lilo

## RAID-1 setup

Using this [guide](http://www.jochem.name/Debian-Sarge-Raid1-mdadm):

	sudo sfdisk -d /dev/sda | sed s/sda/sdb/ > /tmp/sdb
	sudo sfdisk -f /dev/sdb < /tmp/sdb
	sudo mdadm --create /dev/md0 --level=1 --raid-devices=2 /dev/sdb2 missing

